                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="17882946" author="beobal" created="Thu, 19 Sep 2024 09:11:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The 4.1 patch applies trivially to 5.0 and is a no-op for trunk. CI to follow...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17891541" author="beobal" created="Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:19:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The PR contains a cherry-pick from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17178&quot; title=&quot;CEP-10: Simulator Java11 Support&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-17178&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-17178&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to backport jdk11 support to the simulator. This commit &lt;em&gt;only&lt;/em&gt; contains changes to simulator test code and is only needed for 4.1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17894833" author="krummas" created="Fri, 1 Nov 2024 11:47:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17894902" author="beobal" created="Fri, 1 Nov 2024 19:10:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed to cassandra-4.1 and merged to cassandra-5.0 &amp;amp; trunk&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
